==============================================================================
                              Klingon Empire
==============================================================================
         A scenario for the game "-Star_Trek-" by Frank Mathieson
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 50878.5
+++ ADMIRAL VAN DOREEN

Dear Captain T. YUKASAWA,

the Klingon house of Duras has sent a small battle fleet of Klingon
cruisers to the Federation's space to take revenge for Captain J.-L. PICARD
helping Gowron to become leader of the Klingon Empire at stardate
45025.4 .

Take your ship, the Galaxy class star ship USS DURABLE (NCC-1722) and
support the Federation fleet around the USS ENTERPRISE (NCC-1701-E)
against the Klingons.

Good luck, Captain!
