@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Very easy
Solvable with unregistered version: Yes (tested)

8 versus 6 - not that hard, isn't it? This scenario is thought for
beginners and much easier than the standard game and the scenarios
provided with it. You can use it to get familiar with -Star_Trek-.
Experienced users can take it to check the power of their ships
without upgrading it that much first. Should be easy and quick (less
than 20 turns) to win.
_____________________________________________________________________

ENEMY UNITS

8x Klingon Battle Cruiser (K'T'INGA CLASS)     275
_____________________________________________________________________

YOUR UNITS

3x Starbase
USS CAIRO (NCC-42136, EXCELSIOR CLASS)         300
